# Intuit Design System - Radius Token Library

## Primitive Radius Tokens (DO NOT USE DIRECTLY IN PLUGINS)

- `--radius-0`: 0
- `--radius-10`: 2px
- `--radius-20`: 4px
- `--radius-30`: 6px
- `--radius-40`: 8px
- `--radius-50`: 10px
- `--radius-60`: 12px
- `--radius-70`: 14px
- `--radius-80`: 16px
- `--radius-90`: 18px
- `--radius-100`: 20px
- `--radius-110`: 22px
- `--radius-120`: 24px
- `--radius-1000`: 9999px

## Semantic Radius Tokens (USE THESE IN PLUGINS)

### Action
- `--radius-action`: --radius-30 /* Optional radius for action components */

### Container
- `--radius-container-overlay`: --radius-30 /* For containers that overlay on top of other parts of a page. Examples: Tooltip, Toast, Popover, Menu. */

### Content
- `--radius-content-control`: --radius-30 /* For content that a user can control with some form of action that is not a button. Examples: Accordion, Page message, Segmented Button, Toggle */

### Full
- `--radius-full`: --radius-1000 /* Optional radius for pill-shaped or round components, such as Progress bar, Radio, Switch, Avatar */

### Large
- `--radius-large`: --radius-40 /* Optional radius for containers */

### Medium
- `--radius-medium`: --radius-30 /* Optional radius for large components */

### None
- `--radius-none`: --radius-0 /* For remove the radius completely (e.g. 0) */

### Small
- `--radius-small`: --radius-20 /* Default radius size for most components, such as Badge, Buttons, Date Picker, Checkbox, Flyout menu, Tooltip, Icon control */

### Table
- `--radius-table`: --radius-30 /* Radius for all tables including DataGrid. */

### X
- `--radius-x-large`: --radius-60 /* Optional radius for extra large components */
- `--radius-x-small`: --radius-10 /* Optional radius for extra small components */
